---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy | ShopifyCalc" description="Privacy policy for ShopifyCalc — how we collect and use data.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm mb-8"><em>Last updated: April 2026</em></p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">1. Who We Are</h2>
        <p>ShopifyCalc (<strong>shopify-fee-calc.com</strong>) is an independent website providing free shipping rate calculators and fee estimator tools for e-commerce sellers. We are not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to Shopify Inc., USPS, UPS, FedEx, DHL, or any carrier mentioned on this site.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">2. Data We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">We collect minimal data necessary to operate the website:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Usage analytics</strong> — via Google Analytics 4 (GA4). This includes: pages visited, time on site, approximate geographic location (city/country level), browser type, device type, and referral source. This data is anonymized and aggregated.</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies</strong> — GA4 sets first-party cookies (<code>_ga</code>, <code>_ga_*</code>) to distinguish users and sessions. These cookies expire after 2 years and 24 hours respectively.</li>
          <li><strong>IP addresses</strong> — collected by GA4 but anonymized (IP anonymization is enabled). We do not store raw IP addresses.</li>
          <li><strong>Calculator inputs</strong> — all calculator inputs (weight, price, destination) are processed entirely in your browser and are <strong>never sent to our servers</strong>.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">3. How We Use Data</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>To understand which tools and pages are most useful to visitors</li>
          <li>To improve site performance and content quality</li>
          <li>We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties for marketing</li>
          <li>We do <strong>not</strong> use data to identify individual users</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">4. Google Analytics</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">We use Google Analytics 4 (Google LLC, 1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View, CA 94043, USA). Google may transfer data to servers outside the EU/EEA. For details on how Google processes this data, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
        <p>To opt out of GA tracking, you can install the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a> or use browser privacy settings.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">5. Your Rights (GDPR / CCPA)</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">If you are located in the European Union (EU) or California (USA), you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">Since we collect only anonymized analytics data, most individual requests cannot be fulfilled for technical reasons (data is not linked to identifiable individuals). Contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@shopify-fee-calc.com" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">privacy@shopify-fee-calc.com</a> for any requests.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>Google Analytics data is retained for 14 months, after which it is automatically deleted. We do not maintain any independent databases of user activity.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">7. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>This site may contain links to third-party websites (e.g., carrier websites). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy periodically. The "Last updated" date at the top indicates when the most recent changes were made.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">9. Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about this policy: <a href="mailto:privacy@shopify-fee-calc.com" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">privacy@shopify-fee-calc.com</a></p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
